<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f172a">
  <title>Arbeitsplatz Franz</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --glass-bg: rgba(20, 25, 33, 0.7);
      --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --base-text: #e2e8f0;
      --muted-text: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.72);
      --accent: #2dd4bf;
      --accent-soft: rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.18);
      --cyan: #67b9ff;
      --warn: #f59e0b;
      --shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      --panel-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      color: var(--base-text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(103, 185, 255, 0.14), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #07101c 0%, #0d1830 100%);
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6, 12, 24, 0.42), rgba(7, 12, 24, 0.12)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018) 0,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018) 1px,
          transparent 1px,
          transparent 120px
        );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1.4rem 2.6rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }

    .hero,
    .panel,
    .link-card {
      border-radius: 26px;
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      background: var(--glass-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow: var(--panel-shadow);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 2rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.6rem);
      line-height: 0.94;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 10ch;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 58ch;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge::before {
      content: "";
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.1);
    }

    .link-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .link-card {
      min-height: 220px;
      padding: 1.6rem 1.2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .link-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      background: rgba(21, 34, 57, 0.88);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .link-card.primary:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .link-card.secondary:hover {
      border-color: rgba(103, 185, 255, 0.28);
    }

    .mark {
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .secondary .mark {
      background: rgba(103, 185, 255, 0.12);
      color: var(--cyan);
    }

    .meta {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.42rem;
    }

    .group {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 1.32rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hint {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .url {
      color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.58);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 1.4rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-head small {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .step strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      color: var(--base-text);
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .note {
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--warn);
      background: rgba(89, 56, 10, 0.24);
      color: #f7d48c;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      color: #cae7ff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      main {
        padding: 1.3rem 1rem 2rem;
      }

      .hero,
      .panel,
      .link-card {
        border-radius: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">FraWo</span>
      <h1>Arbeitsplatz Franz</h1>
      <p>Direktzugriff auf die benoetigten Apps.</p>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">Nextcloud</span>
        <span class="badge">Paperless</span>
        <span class="badge">Odoo</span>
        <span class="badge">Vault</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="link-grid" aria-label="Franz Direktlinks">
      <a class="link-card primary" href="http://cloud.hs27.internal/">
        <div class="mark">NC</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Arbeit</span>
          <span class="title">Nextcloud</span>
          <span class="hint">Dateien und Ablage.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">cloud.hs27.internal</div>
      </a>

      <a class="link-card primary" href="http://paperless.hs27.internal/accounts/login/">
        <div class="mark">PL</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Arbeit</span>
          <span class="title">Paperless</span>
          <span class="hint">Archiv und Suche.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">paperless.hs27.internal/accounts/login/</div>
      </a>

      <a class="link-card primary" href="http://odoo.hs27.internal/web/login">
        <div class="mark">OD</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Arbeit</span>
          <span class="title">Odoo</span>
          <span class="hint">Betrieb und Kunden.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">odoo.hs27.internal/web/login</div>
      </a>

      <a class="link-card secondary" href="https://vault.hs27.internal/">
        <div class="mark">VA</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Betrieb</span>
          <span class="title">Vault</span>
          <span class="hint">Nur bei Passwortabfrage.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">vault.hs27.internal</div>
      </a>

      <a class="link-card secondary" href="http://cloud.hs27.internal/apps/files/?dir=/Paperless/Eingang">
        <div class="mark">IN</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Dokumente</span>
          <span class="title">Nextcloud Eingang</span>
          <span class="hint">Neue Dokumente.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">cloud.hs27.internal/apps/files/?dir=/Paperless/Eingang</div>
      </a>

      <a class="link-card secondary" href="http://100.99.206.128:8447/franz/">
        <div class="mark">MB</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="group">Mobil</span>
          <span class="title">Franz Mobil Start</span>
          <span class="hint">iPhone ueber Tailscale.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url">100.99.206.128:8447/franz/</div>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Kurz</h2>
        <small>Arbeitsweg</small>
      </div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <strong>Start hier</strong>
          Diese Seite oder der Shortcut ist der Einstieg.
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <strong>Vault nur bei Bedarf</strong>
          <code>Vault</code> nur oeffnen, wenn wirklich ein Passwort gebraucht wird.
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <strong>Kein Nebenpfad</strong>
          Keine lokalen Passwortlisten.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
